thread.title: Three men taken to hospital after pushing burning car from barn fire

author: Danielle Salisbury | Danielle_Salisbury@mlive.com
title: Three men taken to hospital after pushing burning car from barn fire
text: The men, who were not believed to be seriously hurt, succeeded in getting the vehicle out of the structure, but did not save the barn or the vehicle. Fire destroyed the 30-by-72-foot building and all its contents.
